<html>

<head>
    <title> Aggregation Builder - MongoDB</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-gH2yIJqKdNHPEq0n4Mqa/HGKIhSkIHeL5AyhkYV8i59U5AR6csBvApHHNl/vI1Bx" crossorigin="anonymous">
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Bootstrap Static Header -->
    <div style="background: url(https://bootstrapious.com/i/snippets/sn-static-header/background.jpg)"
        class="jumbotron bg-cover text-white">
        <div class="container py-5 text-center">
            <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold">Aggregation Builder | MongoDB</h1>
            <p class="font-italic mb-0">
                Start Building your MongoDB Query for DataBase aggregation, 
            </p>
            
            <a href="/aggregation" role="button" class="btn btn-primary px-5 mt-5">Get Started</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- For Demo Purpose -->
    <div class="container py-5">
        <h2 class="h2 font-weight-bold">Comment faire une requête ?</h2>
        
        <div class="m-4 row">
            <h2 class="mt-3 h3 font-weight-bold">Etape 1 : Utiliser # pour séparer les pipelline</h2>
            <div class="p-3 row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img src="img/separation.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <p class="font-italic text-muted">
                    <li>
                        Supprimer tous les commentaire comme : // Stage 1
                    </li>
                   <li>
                        Supprimer aussi les virgules entre les pipellines
                   </li>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-4 row">
            <h2 class="mt-3 h3 font-weight-bold">Etape 2 : Ne pas oublier les guillemet "" des mots clés</h2>
            <div class="p-3 row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img src="img/mots_cle.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <p class="font-italic text-muted">
                    <li>
                        Les contenus des pipellines doivent respecter le format JSON
                    </li>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="m-4 row">
            <h2 class="mt-3 h3 font-weight-bold">Etape 3 : Verifier le format des ISODate ! </h2>
            <div class="p-3 row">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <img src="img/isodate.png" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <p class="font-italic text-muted">
                    <li>
                        Dans le cas de $lookup, l'utilisation de ISODate doit suivre l'exemple précédent
                    </li>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
            <a class="btn btn-success"href="aggregation">Commencer</a>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</body>

</html>